resources.string: This application is project for class Programming mobile applications, on Faculty of Technical Sciences in Čačak. Creator of this app is Aleksa Grbić, index 31/2019. Whiskey is a luxurious alcoholic beverage produced through the fermentation and distillation of grains, most commonly barley, rye, or corn. It is known for its rich aroma, complex flavor, and long-standing tradition of production. Whiskey can come in different types, such as Scotch, Irish, Bourbon, or Rye, each with its own characteristics and styles. The aging process in wooden barrels contributes to the development of complexity and smoothness in whiskey. Many whiskey enthusiasts enjoy it neat, on the rocks, or as an ingredient in cocktails. This highly esteemed beverage has its place in social gatherings and is also a subject of exploration and appreciation for its diversity.

Ova aplikacija je rađena u okviru predmeta Programiranje mobilnih aplikacija, na Fakultetu tehničkih nauka u Čačku. Kreator ove aplikacije je Aleksa Grbić, indeksa 31/2019.Viski je luksuzni alkoholni napitak koji se proizvodi fermentacijom i destilacijom žitarica, najčešće ječma, raži ili kukuruza. On je poznat po svojoj bogatoj aromi, slojevitom ukusu i dugoj tradiciji proizvodnje. Viski može biti različitih vrsta, kao što su scotch, irish, bourbon ili rye, a svaka vrsta ima svoje karakteristike i stilove. Proces starenja u drvenim bačvama doprinosi razvoju kompleksnosti i mekoće viskija. Mnogi ljubitelji viskija uživaju u njegovom ispijanju "neat" (čistog), s ledom ili kao sastojak u koktelima. Ovaj izuzetno cenjeni piće ima svoje mesto u društvenim okupljanjima, ali i kao predmet istraživanja i uživanja u njegovoj raznolikosti.
